    "description": "<strong>DEADED</strong> Is a Third Person Survival game where you scavenge, build, survive and thrive through the zombie infested post apocalyptic world. With heavy emphasis on physics and ragdoll - block, push and move objects to manipulate zombies to gain an advantage against them. <br><br><strong>Physics and Ragdoll</strong> <br>DEADED aims to create an environment in which realistic zombies interact with. Block door ways with couches, barricade doors with wood and have the ability to push zombies over. These zombies will attack you head on, ignoring objects in their way so use it to your advantage.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305510/extras/bf87034fc00ba9bea609ab6125fa88f3.poster.avif?t=1731262969\" width=590 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305510/extras/bf87034fc00ba9bea609ab6125fa88f3.webm?t=1731262969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305510/extras/bf87034fc00ba9bea609ab6125fa88f3.mp4?t=1731262969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Save Survivors</strong> <br>Save survivros you find throughout the city and assign them jobs at your base to produce valuable resources. Make them cut wood, scavenge scrap piles or set them as a security gaurd to help defend against the undead.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305510/extras/24e9274b1cbbb63fb84c58b233c3bcf6.poster.avif?t=1731262969\" width=590 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305510/extras/24e9274b1cbbb63fb84c58b233c3bcf6.webm?t=1731262969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305510/extras/24e9274b1cbbb63fb84c58b233c3bcf6.mp4?t=1731262969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Scavenge</strong><br>Scavenge the city for valuable loots and rummage through housese to find materials to help you and your community survive. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305510/extras/b07ea242e4c7a6e8c1b732624af8c4f4.poster.avif?t=1731262969\" width=590 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305510/extras/b07ea242e4c7a6e8c1b732624af8c4f4.webm?t=1731262969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305510/extras/b07ea242e4c7a6e8c1b732624af8c4f4.mp4?t=1731262969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Combat</strong><br>Shoot, slice and stomp your way through the infected with a variety of weapons such as the machete and pistol, damage any zombies limb enough and it will pop off!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305510/extras/f7ab48badb4ee751d04d5f4a24bfd00c.poster.avif?t=1731262969\" width=590 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305510/extras/f7ab48badb4ee751d04d5f4a24bfd00c.webm?t=1731262969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305510/extras/f7ab48badb4ee751d04d5f4a24bfd00c.mp4?t=1731262969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>The Fog City</strong><br>With the ever changing fog city, discover a way to navigate through it without getting lost. As with each entry something always changes, and its up to you to find out why and how to solve a route of safety through the city.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305510/extras/4bcf0fa9f650f05b7347617141e9be17.poster.avif?t=1731262969\" width=590 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305510/extras/4bcf0fa9f650f05b7347617141e9be17.webm?t=1731262969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305510/extras/4bcf0fa9f650f05b7347617141e9be17.mp4?t=1731262969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
